From: ilikara <3435193369@qq.com>
Date: Tue, 16 Sep 2025 19:46:42 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] AOSCOS: deps: upgrade mmap-rs to v0.7.0, bump nix to v0.30

Upgrade mmap-rs to GitHub v0.7.0 to pull in nix v0.30 support,
ensuring compatibility with loongarch64 and resolving version conflicts.

Signed-off-by: ilikara <3435193369@qq.com>
---
 Cargo.lock | 29 +++++++++--------------------
 Cargo.toml |  3 +++
 2 files changed, 12 insertions(+), 20 deletions(-)

diff --git a/Cargo.lock b/Cargo.lock
index af5f7ee..5671b4c 100644
--- a/Cargo.lock
+++ b/Cargo.lock
@@ -1861,15 +1861,6 @@ version = "2.7.5"
